abstract: >-
  TF-ChPVK-PV is a Python package and analysis pipeline for
  ML-guided screening of chalcogenide perovskites (ABX3,
  X = S, Se) as solar energy materials. It integrates a
  SISSO-derived tolerance factor, CrystaLLM crystal structure
  generation, a GCNN crystal-likeness scorer, CrabNet bandgap
  prediction, and multi-objective sustainability screening
  (HHI, supply risk, ESG scores) to identify experimentally
  viable absorber candidates for photovoltaic applications.
